snippet.title: Peko Peko Sushi Release PV English
snippet.description:
Peko Peko Sushi, a fast-paced conveyor sushi puzzle game for iOS and Android devices. Serve hungry customers by shuffling sushi about, racking up high scores by stacking plates and acting quick. Unlock new staff and store parts to change the way you play and make it your own. Download now and help Ayame build the greatest sushi restaurant of all time!

KEY FEATURES

- Fast-paced sushi matching fun.
- Hundreds of sushi, store parts, and customers to unlock and choose from.
- Dynamic weather and calendar system that changes with every play.
- Amazing soundtrack and audio to serve sushi to!

iOS (Free): http://tiny.cc/PekoPekoSushi-IOS
Android (Free): http://tiny.cc/PekoPekoSushi-Android
PV: http://tiny.cc/PekoPekoSushi-PV-ENG
Website: http://hanaji.com/pekopekosushi
Press Kit: http://tiny.cc/PekoPekoSushi-PressKit
